title: WELCOME TO PRODENTAL
subtitle: HIGH LEVEL DENTAL CLINIC
text: With more than 20 years of experience in oral health and dentistry, we are launching a new Model Dental Clinic oriented towards excellence, a new concept that brings together quality, price, guarantee and efficiency. Endorsed by the trajectory and permanence in the market since 2001, where we innovated and were pioneers in offering dentistry within everyone's reach, creating the Prodental Dental Clinic Chain, unique in Shopping Centers, today we face this new project in which we decided to reinvent ourselves and take dentistry to a level of superiority
